SMSBOX,provides,an,international,web,based,SMS,distribution,platform,with,operators,in,countries,Users,can,create,single,or,bulk,messages,using,SMSBOX,tools,and,send,SMS,via,email,client,mobile,device,or,even,toolbar,Users,can,also,rent,a,dedicated,phone,number,to,receive,SMS,and,they,can,send,voice,messages,in,the,form,of,vocalized,text,an,uploaded,audio,file,or,a,recorded,voice,The,SMSBOX,API,can,be,integrated,with,other,applications,to,enable,them,to,send,SMS